            android:text="Solution:\n
A) Meow\n
\n
Explanation:\n
The analogy states a relationship between a dog and its sound, which is a bark. Similarly, a cat is often associated with the sound 'meow.' Therefore, the correct answer is A) Meow."
            android:lineSpacingExtra="9dp"
            android:visibility="gone" />


        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/tvLogicalReasoningContent6"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_margin="16dp"
            android:textColor="@color/black"
            android:text="\nQuestion 6:\n
Choose the option that best completes the following pattern:\n
